{"tid":2086032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真愛聯有無諗過鎅建制票？","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T07:18:39.000Z","uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df4fb0176c68a2e8420de91a6819d586ff8c7eb4","tid":2086032,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"想當年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://sc1.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201403/1904001_10152253698539890_1739759120_n.jpg-4WNYvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsc1.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201403%2F1904001_10152253698539890_1739759120_n.jpg-4WNYvH.jpg&h=d7f5cd7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為愛國愛港嘅小市民 投俾更加可以止暴制聯嘅候選人 比起投比而家啲建制飯桶更好啦<br />\n香港而家咁亂，一定要個有Power嘅建設派出嚟話事<br />\n政綱絕對要比而家班建制更激進<br />\n政綱1：香港立即實施單一國藉制，禁止所有人包括官員議員及家屬擁有外國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政綱2：禁止所有不認同共產黨領導的政黨運作，不認同黨等於煽動顛覆國家政權，包括所有要建設民主中國的政黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政綱3：立即對美國英國日本台灣歐盟印度全部實施制裁，禁止這些外國勢力公司在港運作，危害國家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想止暴制聯 係咪應該投佢哋啊<br />\n仲投民建聯？ 係咪想黑暴肆虐多幾年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1832651a1e60b45997377f065bc8d96de421079f","tid":2086032,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:59:41.000Z","msg":"聽日 2pm 好想見到你<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KnaBXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KnaBXr.jpg&h=cd06e4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5ohgXs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5ohgXs.jpg&h=032359c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8Vjvhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h